# System limits - managed by Ansible

# Increase file descriptor limits
* soft nofile 65535
* hard nofile 65535

# Increase process limits
* soft nproc 65535
* hard nproc 65535

# Core dump settings (disabled for production)
* soft core 0
* hard core 0

# Memory lock limits (for Java applications)
* soft memlock unlimited
* hard memlock unlimited
